Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Agent Swarm Module

Provides swarm intelligence and distributed/emergent behavior primitives for agents. Enables robust, scalable, and adaptive multi-agent coordination and emergent behavior.

Advanced features include:
- Emergent behavior and collective intelligence
- Distributed consensus with Byzantine fault tolerance
- Dynamic load balancing and resource optimization
- Adaptive coordination and self-organization
- Fault tolerance with automatic recovery
- Performance monitoring and optimization
- Security with swarm-wide trust management
- Scalable communication and routing
- Advanced analytics and swarm metrics
- Cross-swarm collaboration and federation
:End Note

