Note: Dynamic Swarm Configuration Functions
Process called "calculate_swarm_election_timeout" returns Number:
    Let network_latency be get_network_latency()
    Let base_timeout be network_latency multiplied by 20
    Return base_timeout plus (network_latency multiplied by 10)

Process called "calculate_swarm_heartbeat_interval" returns Number:
    Let election_timeout be calculate_swarm_election_timeout()
    Return election_timeout divided by 5
